OL,3,CSoc Dem's Daniel Ennis elected in
OL,4,CDublin Central by-election
OL,6,FDaniel Ennis has been deemed elected
OL,7,Fin the Dublin Central by-election,
OL,8,Fwith the race in Galway West more
OL,9,Fclosely contested.
OL,11,FMr Ennis, the Social Democrats
OL,12,Fcandidate, said he was "just
OL,13,Fdelighted" after he topped the poll in
OL,14,Fwhat party leader Holly Cairns hailed
OL,15,Fas an "emotional" and "great day for
OL,16,Fthe party.
OL,18,FThe poll topper in Galway West was
OL,19,FIndependent Ireland councillor Noel
OL,20,FThomas, closely followed by Fine Gael
OL,21,Fsenator Sean Kyne.
OL,26,@tD@XOUuD@JO]wD@GOUwD@QO]wD@WOU
