PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779606369
OL,3,CSoc Dem's Daniel Ennis elected in
OL,4,CDublin Central by-election
OL,6,FLabour councillor Helen Ogbu was a
OL,7,Fmore distant third in the constituency
OL,8,Fafter the first count.
OL,10,FConstituents cast their votes on
OL,11,FFriday to fill seats vacated by
OL,12,FCatherine Connolly in Galway West when
OL,13,Fshe became president and former
OL,14,Fminister Paschal Donohoe, who stopped
OL,15,Frepresenting Dublin Central to become
OL,16,Fthe World Bank's chief knowledge
OL,17,Fofficer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
