OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779606369
OL,3,CSoc Dem's Daniel Ennis elected in
OL,4,CDublin Central by-election
OL,6,FMs McDonald said it was "not our day"
OL,7,Fand said political growth sometimes
OL,8,Ftakes "detours".
OL,10,FIn Galway West, Mr Thomas was ahead
OL,11,Fafter the first count with 10,007
OL,12,Fvotes.
OL,14,FThe poll topper is a former Fianna
OL,15,FFail representative and was followed
OL,16,Fby Mr Kyne for Fine Gael on 9,647
OL,17,Ffirst preferences.
OL,26,@nD@YOUnD@eO]pD@GOUpD@OO]
