OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779606369
OL,3,CSoc Dem's Daniel Ennis elected in
OL,4,CDublin Central by-election
OL,6,FTaoiseach and Fianna Fail leader
OL,7,FMicheal Martin was at the Galway Lawn
OL,8,FTennis Club for the count and told
OL,9,Freporters his party has "real
OL,10,Fproblems" with "some constituencies".
OL,12,FThe party lost its deposit over Dublin
OL,13,FCentral candidate John Stephens, who
OL,14,Fwas excluded from the race after count
OL,15,Ftwo.
OL,17,FIn Galway West, his candidate Cillian
OL,18,FKeane had 8.8% of first preferences.
OL,26,@qD@YOUrD@IO]rD@POUrD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
