PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779606369
OL,3,CSoc Dem's Daniel Ennis elected in
OL,4,CDublin Central by-election
OL,6,FMr Martin said the party will
OL,7,F"examine" and "reflect" on the by-
OL,8,Felection results, adding: "We would
OL,9,Fhave preferred a higher percentage
OL,10,Foutcome."
OL,12,FHe added: "We'll do our homework and
OL,13,Fwe always want to do better, and
OL,14,Fthat's our focus."
OL,16,FMr Martin said it was a well-known
OL,17,Fpattern that by-elections do not
OL,18,Fcorrelate with general elections,
OL,19,Fadding that candidates can be shown to
OL,20,Fperform better in subsequent contests.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@IO]oD@OOUoD@WO]pD@[OUrD@IO]tD@
OL,26,AKOUvD@RO]
