OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779606369
OL,3,CSoc Dem's Daniel Ennis elected in
OL,4,CDublin Central by-election
OL,6,FHe said the frontrunners in Galway
OL,7,FWest ` Mr Kyne and Mr Thomas ` had
OL,8,Fgained profile in the previous general
OL,9,Felection.
OL,11,FThe campaign of Gerard "The Monk"
OL,12,FHutch, who has been described in court
OL,13,Fby a judge as the patriarchal
OL,14,Ffigurehead of the Hutch criminal
OL,15,Forganisation, was closely watched in
OL,16,FDublin Central.
OL,18,FHe was eliminated from the race after
OL,19,Fthe seventh count, having not appeared
OL,20,Fat the centre by that time.
OL,26,@sD@XOUsD@aO]
