PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779606369
OL,3,CSoc Dem's Daniel Ennis elected in
OL,4,CDublin Central by-election
OL,6,F"This playing up of him as a major
OL,7,Felectoral force to be reckoned with
OL,8,Fhas not proven correct today," she
OL,9,Fsaid.
